KW  - VAR
KW  - SEM
KW  - Endogenous and exogenous variables
KW  - Intraday relationship
KW  - Index arbitrage
KW  - Market volatility
AB  - We conduct simulations to compare the vector autoregression (VAR) and simultaneous equations models (SEM) for examining temporal relationships among arbitrage spreads, spot price volatility, and futures price volatility. Contrary to Koch (1993), we find that the VAR model can better reveal the underlying process, and that SEM can be misleading and may yield unreliable inferences.
